Class BinaryAttribute

Object
org.apache.spark.ml.attribute.Attribute
org.apache.spark.ml.attribute.BinaryAttribute
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, scala.Serializable
public class BinaryAttribute extends Attribute
A binary attribute. param: name optional name param: index optional index param: values optional values. If set, its size must be 2.
